MEMORANDUM DECISIONS.

THE ATLAS. THE LEONARD J. BUSHBY. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 17, 1905.) No. 49. Appeal from the District Court of the United States for the Eastern District of New York. Avery F. Cushman, for appellant Albert A. Wray, for the Bushby. Le Roy S. Gove, for appellee Follette. Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM.

Decree (115 Fed. 856) affirmed, without interest or costs.
